### Step 3: CSS Code (`styles.css`)
Here’s the CSS file to style your website:

```css
body {
    font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f2f5f8;
}

header {
    background-color: #4a90e2;
    color: white;
    padding: 15px 0;
}

nav ul {
    list-style
